    <p><em>Reflexes (0-4+): 0=Absent, 1+=Diminished, 2+=Normal, 3+=Brisk,
        4+=Clonus. Video demonstrates technique.</em></p>

    <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Reflex</th>
          <th>Nerve Roots</th>
