              <td>"Touch your chin with your chest."
                (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sEhVgHRObQ4&t=420s" class="timestamp">7:00</a> - <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sEhVgHRObQ4&t=425s" class="timestamp">7:05</a>)
